<methods>
<class-id>Author class</class-id> <category>instance variables behavior</category>

<body package="DaskalosUserClasses" selector="instVarTypes">instVarTypes
"resource for Daskalos"
^((Core.Dictionary new) add: (#surname -&gt; Core.String); add: (#birthday -&gt; Core.Date); add: (#name -&gt; Core.String); yourself)</body>
